HybridCrypt — a compact demo of hybrid encryption and text steganography.

Features
- Hybrid encryption: FWHT → AES-256-CBC (data) + RSA (AES key).
- Selectable visual styles for encrypted output (English, Armenian, Russian, Emoji).
- Text steganography: hide/extract secrets inside visible text using zero-width Unicode characters.

Quick start
- Backend:
	cd backend && npm install && npm run dev
- Frontend:
	cd frontend && npm install && npm run dev

Notes
- Steganography uses invisible characters; some editors or clipboard tools strip them. If extraction fails, paste and extract inside the app and use the diagnostics panel.

Tech
- Backend: Node.js, Express, MongoDB
- Frontend: React, Vite, TailwindCSS